flowchart LR
    L[Lock Interface] --> L1[Explicit lock/unlock]
    L --> L2[tryLock / timed lock]
    L --> L3[Interruptible acquisition]
    L --> L4[Multiple Condition queues]
    L --> L5[Optional fairness]

    S[synchronized] --> S1[Implicit monitor management]
    S --> S2[No timed try-acquire API]
    S --> S3[No explicit interruptible acquire]
    S --> S4[Single monitor condition queue]
    S --> S5[Simpler syntax, lower misuse risk]